metadata.description:
A collection of classic electric guitar renders reminiscent of 50s and 60s rock 'n' roll.
Varying in colour, materials, and layout, each of the 90 collectible guitar renders is unique from one another.
Don't miss the chance to own a piece of the first run of Lemon Shaped Rock classic electric guitars.
metadata.name: Classic Electric Guitar #002 - Lemon Shaped Rock
